<item>
            <title>[POOL-187] TestGenericKeyedObjectPool.testMaxTotalLRU method falls in an infinite loops</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/POOL-187</link>
                <project id="12310488" key="POOL">Commons Pool</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;After having restored the Genrics, the TestGenericKeyedObjectPool.testMaxTotalLRU test method is stuck and I didn&apos;t figure out the reason &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/sad.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
That&apos;s why I currently put the @Ignore annotation, so JUnit can continue running, but I need help to fix it.&lt;br/&gt;
I suspect Continuum is stuck too, but I think I don&apos;t have enough karma to unlock it.&lt;br/&gt;
Many thanks in advance!!!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
